<p>Fortune is an <a href="http://systems-analysis.net/application/definition.html">application system</a> for Node.js & web browsers. It provides a data access layer (adapter), business logic layer (transform), and presentation layer (serializer). These layers working together can be used to power real-time (WebSocket) and hypermedia applications (RMM Level 3), including web pages and HTTP APIs that conform to the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HATEOAS">HATEOAS</a> constraint.</p>
